OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teachers at a Catholic school have gone
OL,6, on strike over the cancellation of a   
OL,7, talk by a children's author whose books
OL,8, feature gay characters.                
OL,10,FGovernors of the John Fisher School in 
OL,11,FPurley, Croydon, in south London, voted
OL,12,Fnot to cancel Simon James Green's      
OL,13,Fvisit, contrary to the Archdiocese of  
OL,14,FSouthwark's recommendation.            
OL,16,FTwo governors subsequently resigned and
OL,17,Fthe archdiocese sacked the rest.       
OL,19,FThe school, which is closed due to     
OL,20,Fstaff shortages, is yet to comment.    
